Natural Gas Use

This area of your bill shows you how much natural gas your home used over the last 13 months. You can use your energy use history to:

  • Detect fluctuations
  • Identify months where you use more energy and adjust your budget
  • Forecast your energy use
  • Manage your energy use
expand_more

Monthly Energy Summary

Natural gas use is measured in thousand cubic feet and then billed according to your actual use. For more information on your specific rate, see our Energy Charges Explained page.
